{"tid":1167801,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"報唔報仇好？","createTime":"2019-05-23T09:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T03:15:37.000Z","uid":65433,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc97135fb13cfdf8fdbf306030d92ebc5a658e4","tid":1167801,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:28:32.000Z","msg":"話說尋日我同個同team同事開會傾嘢，佢係個一年前跳槽過嚟嘅半新人，雖然structure上佢唔係直接under我，但我算係條team二號人物。<br />\n<br />\n佢不嬲係啲幾能幹，但係啲自尊心勁強嗰啲人，咁佢有啲嘢做得唔夠好，我有碗話碗，佢竟然就咁嬲9咗我，喺條team其他同事面前黑我面，我攞嘢畀佢唔該都無聲，講嘢又無禮貌，啲同事幾對眼睇住。<br />\n<br />\n其實我想講你如果唔同意我睇法，大可以再同我私底下傾，我不嬲出名好人，但你咁樣係人哋面前落我面，我真係佛都有火。大家之前無牙齒印，我亦唔想一嘢破壞個關係，所以嗰刻忍咗。<br />\n<br />\n但我想講，第一，你最多話我講嘢可以唔好咁直接，但我講嘅嘢全部都係事實。第二，你有無諗過我同team head 多年戰友加friend底，我要報仇真係易過借火，放工同team head飲嘢時喺佢耳邊講兩句嘢你就周身蟻，我真係唔明點解佢好似完全無呢個危機意識咁...<br />\n<br />\n我知道而家啲後生EQ係低，需要時間成長，但我亦都好唔順氣，谷住谷住。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係我，你會點做？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲後生仔咁唔識做人，唔教訓下唔得，否則之後好難食住佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得饒人處且饒人，大家仲要日見夜見，一次半次無謂計較"},{"pid":"37e8d9733befbb9a10fea0e12f0dfd92abd12dce","tid":1167801,"uid":71508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"寬恕係最大嘅美德<br />\n以德報怨啦後生仔"},{"pid":"b90ad7e6ac74327b23f252be0f6ee67f4c7ac912","tid":1167801,"uid":121504,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:13:51.000Z","msg":"出名好人但想報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7356ea7180bb00b608f53032fbc7f483ea4a5c","tid":1167801,"uid":127272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/de2WL72.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fde2WL72.gif&h=1a6822e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c4b7be812b0f283cbf7cf08662d33b4b2df1171","tid":1167801,"uid":225760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c864de1a013672ffa5269f232626dd5f3fcb84f","tid":1167801,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"咁都忍得屎都食得"},{"pid":"0f297622f369d858595f7d7510a91f8dd9a9b4ab","tid":1167801,"uid":38358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:17:28.000Z","msg":"你咁都唔識處理要上黎問人，好意思話自己係Second head?"},{"pid":"f9b357f2507aad855e7a372bd6438ebd3674a8f8","tid":1167801,"uid":187072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:19:09.000Z","msg":"報咪報囉，驚你有牙？"},{"pid":"eb3fa580904924e8bcaed530a2376928975b7cf1","tid":1167801,"uid":87988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0f297622f369d858595f7d7510a91f8dd9a9b4ab","tid":1167801,"uid":38358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:17:28.000Z","msg":"你咁都唔識處理要上黎問人，好意思話自己係Second head?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"second head or seven head"},{"pid":"38739817920459a1dfcd7930050d42f48ca65dd3","tid":1167801,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"一個新來既你都搞唔掂<br />\n要開post問<br />\n垃圾<br />\n不如你辭職啦"},{"pid":"e7607965ae22ed7096b4bc64a0359f955d0ca94f","tid":1167801,"uid":83386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"炒佢輕鬆"},{"pid":"7dc31bb5bbb19a3ce736b2a9daf6bc50a8500e3f","tid":1167801,"uid":90060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"佢真係有料，你又高grade過佢，不如諗計湊好佢，又少個敵人"},{"pid":"361467a1964db3d5c1667f6377d3f469a284e6d5","tid":1167801,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:14:02.000Z","msg":"唔發火當我病貓"},{"pid":"a0896c0dbd665570df58cf5043c1260521e19e44","tid":1167801,"uid":187072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:15:37.0